org.spongepowered.api.data.key

Class KeyFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongepowered.api.data.key.KeyFactory

  • public final class KeyFactory
extends Object
    A factory of Keys, useful for both the implementation of SpongeAPI, and for plugins wishing to provide their own Keys without having to remain afraid of having to cast back and forth.

      • makeSingleKey

        public static <E,V extends BaseValue<E>> Key<V> makeSingleKey(Class<E> elementClass,
                                                              Class<V> valueClass,
                                                              DataQuery query)
        Creates a new Key with the provided E element class and V Value class along with the provided default DataQuery to be used with the generated Key.

        Note that Keys are not registered, but it is recommended to avoid generating Keys of potentially conflicting DataQuery(s).

        Type Parameters:
        E - The type of element
        V - The type of value
        Parameters:
        elementClass - The element class
        valueClass - The value class
        query - The query
        Returns:
        The generated key
